    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/d96e9b4e9dae7b21e56ca9981b01247c.poster.avif?t=1741914392\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/d96e9b4e9dae7b21e56ca9981b01247c.webm?t=1741914392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/d96e9b4e9dae7b21e56ca9981b01247c.mp4?t=1741914392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公在生活中总是莫名其妙地被困在密室中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单却有意味深长的谜题层出不穷，解开谜底的瞬间令人倍感畅快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■第一章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱舞台设在一家大型连锁汉堡店——熊当劳汉堡。主人公在店内小憩醒来后，发现四周空无一人，店员和顾客都消失无踪，而出口的门也无法打开？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界一隅的连锁店中，一场逃脱剧即将拉开帷幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/57cd875ca234236ba79ef04d620d4d91.poster.avif?t=1741914392\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/57cd875ca234236ba79ef04d620d4d91.webm?t=1741914392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196770/extras/57cd875ca234236ba79ef04d620d4d91.mp4?t=1741914392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了全3D画面和各种巧妙机关，操作体验顺畅，支持多种游戏模式，包括多重结局。配备便条、相机功能等，确保从新手到逃脱专家都能简单地享受“解谜”乐趣的逃脱游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各个故事独立成章，可从随意情境开始体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■欢迎参与 Let's Plays！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎随时通过我们的官方账号与我们联系！</p>",
